8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); text-decoration: underli=
ne;">AI models collapse when trained on recursively generated data</a></str=
ong></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 2=
6px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><em>Shumailov, Shumaylov, Zhao, Papernot, Anderso=
